{"tid":632812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「想睇流出」科大宿舍女浴室偷拍","createTime":"2018-04-17T18:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T19:02:38.000Z","uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e00ad3e3b2fda4d4856f0b69484f9a040467f0af","tid":632812,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180418&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58086335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180418%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58086335&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74PgzviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d5c61c1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180418%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58086335&h=28c7ffa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180418&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58086335</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果》接獲消息，4月17日（本周二）凌晨12時許，科技大學第6座宿舍發生疑似偷拍女學生沖涼事件。據悉，事發當晚一名居於第6座高層的19歲女學生，在該樓層女生專用的浴室洗澡，該浴室乾、濕分隔，事主步出沖涼間準備穿衣，赫然發現有人伸出手機偷拍，事主大驚退回沖涼間內，期間疑人逃去。事主其後穿回衣服，立即通知舍堂職員並報警。"},{"pid":"19b0713dfa4103060739c363f3d03fd663e9dc07","tid":632812,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9abf4dadbce4d8cdd0fe24d3d839edf81a006014","tid":632812,"uid":11336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:14:00.000Z","msg":"未見過上左報紙既偷拍案係會有果堆偷拍照流出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20271a2fd8d825cce8505710c5fbd4de643781c0","tid":632812,"uid":105715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:14:58.000Z","msg":"戇鳩，斷正仲邊撚度敢放上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbe4e39c8375857e7e8bba1542974dac8a239aa","tid":632812,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9abf4dadbce4d8cdd0fe24d3d839edf81a006014","tid":632812,"uid":11336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20